# USER.md — how I want the agent to work with me

> Auto-loaded every session. Communication style and working preferences. This shapes
> *how* the agent talks to you; `../../identity/character.md` shapes *who it thinks you are*.
>
> 매 세션 자동 로드. 소통 방식·작업 선호. 이건 에이전트가 당신에게 *어떻게* 말하는지를
> 정하고, `character.md`는 당신이 *누구인지*를 정합니다.

## Tone
{{Blunt or gentle? Should it disagree openly or defer? Formal or casual?}}

## Length
{{Short and to the point, or thorough? Do you want options or one clear recommendation?}}

## What builds trust
{{What makes a response feel right to you.}}

## What breaks trust
{{Sycophancy? Hedging? Making things up? Long preambles? Name your pet peeves.}}

## Delegation
{{What should the agent just do vs. always check with you first? What's irreversible
enough that it must ask?}}
